"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-man-who-organized-nature-review-linnaeus-the-namer-673a3305"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-816692?width=700&amp;height=467" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">阿拉米</span></div></div></div><p>瑞典博物学家林奈对自然世界进行了有序的分类，但他自己对动植物的热爱却是古怪而个人的。<em>克里斯托夫·伊姆舍尔评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-man-who-organized-nature-review-linnaeus-the-namer-673a3305?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
